FBIS3-13061 "drnes046_r_94003" FBIS-NES-94-046 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Mar 1994 India Delhi Protests to Pakistan, Bangladesh on Terrorism BK0803163294 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1530 GMT 8 Mar 94 BK0803163294 Delhi All India Radio Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] India has lodged a strong protest with Pakistan and Bangladesh following the arrests of some of their nationals connected with terrorist activities in India. An External Affairs Ministry spokesman said in New Delhi that the matter of four Pakistani and one Bangladeshi national apprehended by the police was taken up with their missions in New Delhi yesterday.
